{"id": 57748, "date": "2025-07-17T04:00:45", "date_gmt": "2025-07-17T11:00:45", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57748"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T10:32:53", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T17:32:53", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-17-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/17/kingdom-of-days-july-17-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 17"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles headline two shows at the Off Broad Street Coffee House in Red Bank, New Jersey. Jeannie Clark opens for the band; she will later join Dr. Zoom and the Sonic Boom as a Zoomette.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3061\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0717/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?fit=800%2C478&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,478\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0717\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?fit=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?fit=758%2C453&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3061 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?resize=758%2C453&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0717.jpg?resize=768%2C459&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays their third of six consecutive nights at the Pandemonium in Wanamassa, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill headlines at Asbury Park&#8217;s Sunshine In, with a setlist that features &#8220;Garden State Parkway Blues,&#8221; &#8220;Sherlock Goes Home,&#8221; and &#8220;KT-88.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/40fj8jiZGsM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19634\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1970-07-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?fit=1072%2C1747&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1072,1747\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1970-07-17\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?fit=184%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?fit=628%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19634 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?resize=758%2C1235&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1235\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?w=1072&amp;ssl=1 1072w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?resize=184%2C300&amp;ssl=1 184w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?resize=628%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 628w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?resize=768%2C1252&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1970-07-17.png?resize=943%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 943w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play two shows at Le Garage in Spray Beach, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11328\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/garage717/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?fit=327%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"327,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"garage717\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?fit=196%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?fit=327%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11328 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?resize=327%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"327\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?w=327&amp;ssl=1 327w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/garage717.jpg?resize=196%2C300&amp;ssl=1 196w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 327px) 100vw, 327px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band work on &#8220;Cindy&#8221; during a recording session at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Joe Grushecky and the Iron City Houserockers on stage for the first time when Joe plays Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank.</p>\n<div id=\"v-vfcrn5r7-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/vfcrn5r7?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>On Night Two at the Rosemont Horizon near Chicago, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out&#8221; and &#8220;Because the Night.&#8221; Watch news coverage and footage below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kkUCWM9MA5k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19638\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?fit=851%2C348&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"851,348\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-17\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?fit=300%2C123&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?fit=758%2C310&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19638 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?resize=758%2C310&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?w=851&amp;ssl=1 851w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?resize=300%2C123&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-17.png?resize=768%2C314&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>The Tunnel of Love Tour arrives in Munich, where &#8220;Badlands&#8221; makes its tour premiere.</p>\n<div id=\"v-Hg1d3CbK-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/Hg1d3CbK?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-xZriKscC-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/xZriKscC?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Night Two (of ten!) at the legendary Giants Stadium stand of the Rising Tour is a standard one, but shake-ups are on their way.</p>\n<div id=\"v-woWaq6U5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/woWaq6U5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2004:\u00a0</strong>Bruce, Patti, and Soozie join Joe Grushecky and the Houserockers on stage at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11333\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/grusheck/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?fit=500%2C333&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,333\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 10D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1090117115&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;200&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0055555555555556&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"grusheck\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?fit=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?fit=500%2C333&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11333 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?resize=500%2C333&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/grusheck.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19639\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2004-07-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?fit=1314%2C1749&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1314,1749\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2004-07-17\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?fit=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?fit=758%2C1009&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19639 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?resize=758%2C1009&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1009\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?w=1314&amp;ssl=1 1314w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?resize=225%2C300&amp;ssl=1 225w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?resize=769%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 769w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?resize=768%2C1022&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2004-07-17.png?resize=1154%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1154w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2008:\u00a0</strong>The Magic Tour&#8217;s Spanish leg continues with a show in Madrid, featuring a rare performance of &#8220;Cover Me.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xzVzqJEkbJ4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bA7WK-awFnY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance at J.T. Bowen and The Sensational Soul Cruisers&#8217; tribute to Clarence Clemons at The Wonder Bar in Asbury Park. The setlist highlights: long-awaited returns of &#8220;Action in the Streets&#8221; (the first in 34 years) and &#8220;Savin&#8217; Up&#8221; (the first in 24 years).</p>\n<div id=\"v-9neskCQb-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9neskCQb?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19640\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2011-07-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?fit=2072%2C1524&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2072,1524\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2011-07-17\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?fit=300%2C221&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?fit=758%2C557&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19640 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=758%2C558&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"558\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?w=2072&amp;ssl=1 2072w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=300%2C221&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=1024%2C753&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=768%2C565&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=1536%2C1130&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2011-07-17.png?resize=2048%2C1506&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>&#8220;Before we were so rudely interrupted&#8230;&#8221;<strong>\u00a0</strong>Bruce picks up in Dublin where he left off&#8211;or rather, was cut off&#8211;at Hyde Park, bringing his own mock generator on stage, flipping the switch to &#8220;ON&#8221; and finishing &#8220;Twist and Shout&#8221; from the previous show. He then launches directly into &#8220;I Fought the Law,&#8221; a very appropriate tour premiere. Other tour premieres include &#8220;I&#8217;m a Rocker&#8221; and &#8220;My Hometown.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Ehdf2SbIDI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6R68gn0eE2E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52528\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_leader_post_2012_07_20_15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?fit=2282%2C2501&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2282,2501\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?fit=274%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?fit=758%2C831&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52528 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?resize=758%2C831&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"831\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?w=2282&amp;ssl=1 2282w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?resize=274%2C300&amp;ssl=1 274w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?resize=934%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 934w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?resize=768%2C842&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?resize=1402%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1402w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Leader_Post_2012_07_20_15.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong>Netflix films a special invitation-only performance of <em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. The show features two special encores (&#8220;The Ghost of Tom Joad&#8221; and &#8220;Long Time Comin'&#8221;) and will be released on the streaming service to much acclaim later in the year.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/M1xDzgob1JI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York city, In attendance tonight: Danny DeVito and Adam Duritz.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"36020\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2021-07-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/2021-07-17.jpg?fit=309%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"309,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2021-07-17\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/2021-07-17.jpg?fit=185%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-